## âœ… Summary Table

| Function        | What it does                         | Stops with        |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------ | ----------------- |
| `setTimeout()`  | Runs a function **once after delay** | `clearTimeout()`  |
| `setInterval()` | Runs a function **repeatedly**       | `clearInterval()` |

